HeroRat is a revolutionnary system to manage and control remote computers.
It works under Windows, Linux and Mac OS.

"One tool to rules them all" would have said Frodon if he had viewed this.

The 'HeroRat' folder contains the manager, this is what you need to encrypt and put on your web server.
The 'HeroRat_loader' folder is what you share with your customer. This is basically is simple login which download and decrypt the previous project.
The 'HeroRat_Server' folder is the app that should be installed on each computer you want to control.
The 'HeroRat_WebValidation' folder is what you should put on your website to generate new manager clients.